            <characteristic name="Declare" typeId="bad3-f9c5-ba46-18cb">Pick a visible enemy unit within 10&quot; of this unit to be the target</characteristic>
            <characteristic name="Effect" typeId="b6f1-ba36-6cd-3b03">Roll a dice. If the roll exceeds the target&apos;s Health characteristic, 1 model in the target unit is slain.</characteristic>
            <characteristic name="Keywords" typeId="12e8-3214-7d8f-1d0f">**^^Rampage^^**</characteristic>
