                      <characteristics>
                        <characteristic name="Timing" typeId="652c-3d84-4e7-14f4">Your Movement Phase</characteristic>
                        <characteristic name="Declare" typeId="bad3-f9c5-ba46-18cb">Pick a friendly **Awakened Wyldwood** to be the target.</characteristic>
                        <characteristic name="Effect" typeId="b6f1-ba36-6cd-3b03">Remove the target from the battlefield and set it up again wholly within 6&quot; of this unit, more than 1&quot; from all enemy units and other terrain features and more than 3&quot; from all objectives. Then, remove this unit from the battlefield and set it up again wholly within the **creeping overgrowth** and more than 9&quot; from all enemy units.</characteristic>
