                        <characteristic name="Effect" typeId="fd7f-888d-3257-a12b">When using the &apos;Endless Growth&apos; ability, add **X** to the D3 roll for this unit, where **X** is the number of terrain features within 12&quot; of this unit that have a friendly **overgrown token**.</characteristic>
